quran[9{c,v,t}:
34,40,"aur jis din woh tamam insanon ko jama kere ga phir firshton se pouchye ga"" kya yeh log tumhari hi ibadat kya karte thay? """
34,41,"to woh jawab den ge ke"" pak hai aap ki zaat, hamara talluq to aap se hai nah ke inn logon se darasal yeh hamari nahi balkay junoo ki ibadat karte thay, un mein se aksar unhi par imaan laaye hue thay """
34,42,( uss waqt hum kahin ge ke ) aaj tum mein se koi nah kisi ko faida pouncha sakta hai nah nuqsaan aur zaalmon se hum keh den ge ke ab chako is azaab jahannum ka maza jisay tum jhatlaya karte thay
34,43,"inn logon ko jab hamari saaf saaf ayaat sunai jati hain to yeh kehte hain ke"" yeh shakhs to bas yeh chahta hai ke tum ko unn mabodon se bur-ghashta kar day jin ki ibadat tumahray baap dada karte aeye hain"" aur kehte hain ke"" yeh ( quran ) mehez aik jhoot hai ghara howa"" inn kafiroon ke samnay jab haq aaya to inhen ne keh diya ke"" yeh to Sarih jaadoo hai """
34,44,halaank nah hum ne inn logon ko pehlay koi kitaab di thi ke yeh usay parhte hon aur nah tum se pehlay un ki taraf koi mutnabba karne wala bheja tha
34,45,inn se pehlay guzray hue log jhutla chuke hain jo kuch hum ne unhen diya tha uss ke ushar Ashir ko bhi yeh nahi puhanche hain magar jab unhon ne mere Rasolo-n ko jhatlaya to dekh lau ke meri saza kaisi sakht thi
34,46,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn se kaho ke"" mein tumhe bas aik baat ki nasiyaat karta hon khuda ke liye tum akailey akailey aur do do mil kar apna dimagh lrhao aur socho, tumahray sahib mein aakhir aisi konsi baat hai jo junoon ki ho? woh to aik sakht azaab ki aamad se pehlay tum ko mutnabba karne wala hai """
34,47,"inn se kaho,"" agar mein ne tum se koi ajar manga hai to woh tum hi ko mubarak rahay mera ajar to Allah ke zimma hai aur woh har cheez par gawah hai """
34,48,"un se kaho"" mera rab ( mujh par ) haq ka alqa karta hai aur woh tamam posheeda haqeeqaton ka jan-nay wala hai """
